               <provenance>The names Walda Māryām, ʾabuna Gabra Śǝllāse
                     are added by secondary hand (s. supplication formulas on 4rb, 5rb, 8ra, 23va, 82vb, etc.), over erasures, possible in place
                     of original name(s). Besides, other individuals are mentioned in the
                     supplication formulas: ʾAbuna Gabra
                     Giwärgis/Giyorgis (8ra), Walda Gabrǝʾel (7ra), Walda ʾAmlāk (7ra),
                     Walatta Madḫǝn (24ra), Walatta Māryām (82vb), Walatta Kidān (82vb), Walda Ḥawāryāt (82vb), Haylä
                     Māryām (82vb), Walatta Kidān (82vb), Walatta Yoḥannǝs (82vb), Walatta Śǝllāse (82vb).</provenance></history>
